    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Classify with AI\n\nLLM classification into: Mention, Question, Complaint (+fallback). Output port order matches this list.\n\nPorts: ①→ Store as Mention · ②→ Store as Question, Capture Failure Context · ③→ Store as Complaint · ④→ Alert Gmail — Other\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail",
